    <h1><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Quick Start Guide</h1>
    <p class="help-intro">Get up and running with NonProfit Finance in 10 minutes!</p>
    
    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div class="help-step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
            <h2>Set Up Your Organization</h2>
            <p>First, configure your organization details in Settings.</p>
            
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to <strong>Settings</strong> in the sidebar</li>
                <li>Enter your organization name (e.g., "Sample Fire Department")</li>
                <li>Add your EIN (Tax ID) - format: XX-XXXXXXX</li>
                <li>Set your fiscal year start month</li>
                <li>Click <strong>Save Organization Settings</strong></li>
            </ol>
            
            <div class="help-tip">
                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                <strong>Tip:</strong> Your EIN is required for Form 990 compliance. Find it on your 501(c)(3) determination letter.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div class="help-step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
            <h2>Create Your Accounts</h2>
            <p>Accounts (formerly called Funds) represent where your money is held.</p>
            
            <div class="help-example">
                <h4>Common Nonprofit Accounts:</h4>
                <table class="help-table">
                    <tr>
                        <th>Account Name</th>
                        <th>Type</th>
                        <th>Purpose</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>General Fund</td>
                        <td>Unrestricted</td>
                        <td>Day-to-day operations</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Building Fund</td>
                        <td>Restricted</td>
                        <td>Station improvements</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Equipment Fund</td>
                        <td>Restricted</td>
                        <td>Apparatus and gear</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Training Fund</td>
                        <td>Temporarily Restricted</td>
                        <td>Firefighter training</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <ol>
                <li>Go to <strong>Accounts</strong> in the sidebar</li>
                <li>Click <strong>Add Account</strong></li>
                <li>Enter name, type, and optional target balance</li>
                <li>Click <strong>Save</strong></li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div class="help-step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
            <h2>Set Up Categories</h2>
            <p>Categories classify your income and expenses for reporting.</p>
            
            <div class="help-example">
                <div class="two-column">
                    <div>
                        <h4>?? Income Categories</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Donations - Individual</li>
                            <li>Donations - Corporate</li>
                            <li>Grants</li>
                            <li>Fundraising Events</li>
                            <li>Membership Dues</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>?? Expense Categories</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Equipment & Apparatus</li>
                            <li>Training & Education</li>
                            <li>Utilities</li>
                            <li>Insurance</li>
                            <li>Maintenance & Repairs</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="help-note">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                <strong>Note:</strong> The app comes with default categories. Customize them to match your needs!
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Step 4 -->
    <div class="help-step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
            <h2>Record Your First Transaction</h2>
            <p>Now let's record some financial activity!</p>
            
            <h4>Quick Add (Fastest Method):</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>N</kbd> or click <strong>Quick Add</strong></li>
                <li>Select Income or Expense</li>
                <li>Enter amount and description</li>
                <li>Choose category</li>
                <li>Click <strong>Save Transaction</strong></li>
            </ol>
            
            <h4>Full Transaction Form:</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Go to <strong>Transactions</strong></li>
                <li>Click <strong>Add Transaction</strong></li>
                <li>Fill in all details (date, amount, category, account, payee)</li>
                <li>Optionally link to a donor or grant</li>
                <li>Click <strong>Save</strong></li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Step 5 -->
    <div class="help-step">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-content">
            <h2>Add Your Donors</h2>
            <p>Track who gives to your organization.</p>
            
            <ol>
                <li>Go to <strong>Donors</strong></li>
                <li>Click <strong>Add Donor</strong></li>
                <li>Enter name, type (Individual, Business, Foundation), and contact info</li>
                <li>Save the donor</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div class="help-tip">
                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                <strong>Why track donors?</strong> 
                <ul>
                    <li>Generate tax receipts automatically</li>
                    <li>Track giving history</li>
                    <li>Identify major donors</li>
                    <li>Report on donor retention</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Step 6 -->
    <div class="help-step">
        <div class="step-number">6</div>
        <div class="step-content">
            <h2>Explore the Dashboard</h2>
            <p>Your command center for financial overview.</p>
            
            <div class="dashboard-preview">
                <div class="preview-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    <span>Income vs Expenses Trend</span>
                </div>
                <div class="preview-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
                    <span>Total Cash Balance</span>
                </div>
                <div class="preview-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                    <span>Restricted Funds %</span>
                </div>
                <div class="preview-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    <span>Recent Transactions</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
